text:
Is there a way to have an if statement on an email module that can read the email subscription type on a per email basis?

i.e. depending on if say "Transactional" is selected or "Newsletter" - I'd like some legal text to switch out on the footer.

It would be great to be able to do this with an if statement. I did something similar with the office locations but am not sure what to reference for the subscriptions types.

my module code I used for the office locations is:
{% if site_settings.office_location_name is string_containing "REGIONAL" %}
text for regional
  {% elif site_settings.office_location_name is string_containing "NATIONAL" %}
	text for national
{% else %}

{% endif %}

hoping I can use the same or be shown a better way :slightly_smiling_face:
